name: initializeWithContext
description: Initializes AgoraRtcEngine.Before calling other APIs, you must call initializeWithContext to create an AgoraRtcEngine object.

parameters.config: Configurations for the AgoraRtcEngine instance. For details, see RtcEngineContext.

returns:
0(ERR_OK): Success.
       < 0: Failure.
  -1(ERR_FAILED): A general error occurs (no specified reason).
  -2(ERR_INVALID_ARGUMENT): An invalid parameter is used.
  -7(ERR_NOT_INITIALIZED): The SDK is not initialized.
  -22(ERR_RESOURCE_LIMITED): The resource is limited. The SDK fails to allocate resources because your app uses too many system resources or system resources are insufficient.
  -101(ERR_INVALID_APP_ID): The App ID is invalid.
